Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:46.87,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}就算Piece全部集齊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.89,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}この手で導かなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.89,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}也得用這雙手去指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:52.61,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大事な今を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:52.61,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}把重要的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.08,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}手放すのは怖いよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.08,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}放手離去是很可怕的吧
